Blinkit Sales Analytics Dashboard
This project is an interactive Power BI dashboard built to analyze sales performance, customer behavior, and outlet insights for a retail/grocery platform (Blinkit). 
The dashboard provides a comprehensive view of business metrics such as total sales, average sales, product distribution, and outlet performance.
It enables users to explore data dynamically using filters like outlet location, size, and type. The dashboard highlights key trends such as sales growth over time, item category performance, and outlet-level contributions, helping stakeholders make data-driven decisions.

Key insights include:

Total sales of $1.20M with an average sale of $141
Performance comparison across outlet tiers (Tier 1, Tier 2, Tier 3)
Category-wise sales distribution (Fruits, Snacks, Household, etc.)
Impact of outlet size and type on revenue
Customer rating trends and item visibility analysis

This project demonstrates skills in data cleaning, data modeling, DAX, and data visualization using Power BI.
